### Get Deal Quote Requests by Deal ID (for Suppliers)

### This endpoint allows suppliers to see all quote requests for their specific deal

GET http://localhost:5050/api/deal-quote-request/deal/6863ca7e5a2b0f7e5c8aa696
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SELLER_TOKEN_HERE

### Example with query parameter style (if you prefer)
GET http://localhost:5050/api/deal-quote-request/deal/6863ca7e5a2b0f7e5c8aa696?dealId=6863ca7e5a2b0f7e5c8aa696
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SELLER_TOKEN_HERE

### Response will include:
# - All quote requests for this specific deal
# - Buyer information for each request
# - Request details (quantity, shipping, payment terms)
# - Status of each request
# - Seller responses if any

### Authorization Check:
# - Only the supplier who created the deal can access
# - Verified by checking deal.productId.createdBy === sellerId
